description:
Shake it up with these Eggman Maracas!
This accessory changes Amigo's maracas into maracas that look like Eggman from Sonic the Hedgehog!

This item is included in the Tails Costume & Accessories Pack.
Purchasing the Tails Costume & Accessories Pack will make this accessory available for your Amigo in the shop menu.
name: Eggman Maracas
